net.tridentsdk.inventory

Interface Inventory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TridentInventory

    @ThreadSafe
public interface Inventory
    Represents an inventory or inventory that is opened to players
    Since:
    0.3-alpha-DP
    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
